definition
let D be non empty set ;
let r, f, CR be File of D;
pred r is_a_record_of f,CR means :: FILEREC1:def 1
( ( CR ^ r is_substring_of addcr (f,CR),1 or addcr (f,CR) is_preposition_of ) & r is_terminated_by CR );
end;
